Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:39.07,OP-EN-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\fad(100,100)}Tell me what's your name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:47.90,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\fad(100,100)}また惹かれあっては
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:53.46,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\fad(100,100)}比べあうことで貶した
